%F A320857 a(n) = -Sum_{primes p<=n} Kronecker(-2,p) = -Sum_{primes p<=n} A188510(p).
%e A320857 Pi(8,1)(200) = 8, Pi(8,5)(200) = 13, Pi(8,3)(200) = Pi(8,7)(200) = 12, so a(200) = 13 + 12 - 8 - 12 = 5.
